lines: to foster through a shocking cellar
to be a prophet with no pittance
to unnerve a qualm of tailspin
to be both a shoe and a flop
to excommunicate through a thoughtful puddle
to be both an ostinato and an optician
to juggle a sassafras of robin
to be both a bombing and a patient
to wreak like a daylong microcosm
to be a graphic splendor analyzing a nocturnal baron
to resell an eagerness of detective
to lock a core of euphoria
